claim: Jeff Hardy is a cruiserweight wrestler.
premise_source_doc_sentence: As a tag team wrestler , Hardy is a 12-time world tag team champion , having held six World Tag Team Championships , two WWE  (  Raw  )  Tag Team Championships , ROH World Tag Team Championship , one WCW Tag Team Championship , and two TNA World Tag Team Championships  (  the first man to have held all said titles , followed by Jeff  )  .
